  "body": "**üßê Motivation**\r\n<!-- Is your feature request related to a specific problem? Is it just a crazy idea? Tell us about it! -->\r\n\r\nI have some custom logic, whereby there is a mix of an Ownable and AccessControl, such that the `owner()` will have \r\nevery role by default. \r\n\r\n**üìù Details**\r\n\r\nTo do this, I need to override the `hasRole` in the `AccessControl` library. however, it is impossible right now because it is set to private. So making this `internal virtual` would be perfect.\r\n\r\n<!-- Make sure that you have reviewed the OpenZeppelin Contracts Contributor Guidelines. -->\r\n<!-- https://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-contracts/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md -->\r\n",
